{
 "name": "RPlog_Nar_Shaddaa_-_Sabrina_s_Rescue_2",
 "title": "Nar Shaddaa - Sabrina's Rescue (Part 2)",
 "summary": "As the Voidstalker sits on the pad near Galla the Hutt's facility, Luke Skywalker, the Jedi Ai'kani, and the Horansi warrior Snarl plan their infiltration using R2-D2's heat-signature scans showing twenty guards and a single cargo entrance. Snarl chafes at Luke's insistence on giving the criminals a chance rather than fighting outright, but defers to her cousin's command. Disguising themselves as spacers, the trio approach two guards whom Luke and Ai'kani bend with the Force while Snarl plays a harmless pet, gaining entry. Inside, a Rodian boss recognizes Luke Skywalker and the cover is blown, erupting into a saber-and-blaster melee against fifteen of Galla's thugs as the team fights toward Sabrina.",
